{"id":"6621","name":"bright-early-manic-tuesday-edition-2","title":"Bright &amp; Early: Manic Tuesday Edition","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2011-03-01T10:30:00-06:00","tags":["bna","bring your guns to work","fire drill","free pancakes","green hills mall","ihop","nashville international airport","rta","satellite box office","springfield","tpac","ymca"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/manieldack/5479930387/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm6.static.flickr.com/5171/5479930387_b645c88727.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\"></a></p><p>Good morning, Nashville. We&#x2019;re running behind, so you know the drill. Your abbreviated Bright &amp; Early:</p><ul><li>Sun is in the forecast today! Lots of sun! Hallelujah. &#xA0;[<a href=\"http://nashvillewx.com/2011/03/patchy-fog-and-a-few-clouds-this-morning-plenty-of-sun-the-rest-of-the-day/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillewx.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Nashville WX</a>]</li><li>If you see a big disturbance and a bunch of flashing emergency lights around the airport today and tomorrow, don&#x2019;t freak out! They&#x2019;re just doing their annual live fire training. That said, traffic could be moving a little slower there this week so plan ahead. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/story/14161362/airport-training-may-slow-traffic\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li><li>A bill moving through the legislature could allow folks to pack heat in the workplace. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/story/14161378/handguns-could-be-allowed-at-work\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li><li>Have you heard? It&#x2019;s Free Pancake Day at IHOP! For charity, of course. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/story/14161325/free-pancakes-to-help-those-in-need\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li><li>So after you finish stuffing yourself with pancakes, you can read this story about how the YMCA has seen a 22,000-person attendance increase over this time last year. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/story/14161389/ymca-sees-increase-in-attendance-in-2011\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li><li>TPAC has opened up a brand new satellite box office at the Green Hills Mall, and they&#x2019;re offering buy-one-get-one-free tickets to select performances to celebrate. [<a href=\"http://www.outandaboutnewspaper.com/article/4614\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.outandaboutnewspaper.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Out &amp; About</a>]</li><li>The Regional Transportation Authority saw such a demand for the hour-long bus route from Springfield that they decided to make it permanent. [<a href=\"http://wpln.org/?p=24566\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;wpln.org&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WPLN</a>]</li></ul><p><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/manieldack/5479930387/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Daniel Mack</a></em>.</p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2010/05/25/bright-early-manic-tuesday-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: Manic Tuesday Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: Manic Tuesday Edition</a></li></ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}